reviewText: I love the stones and the instruction. Patty is great.
Can't find a player to play it
It was what I was looking for in a DVD.

This is a great introduction to hot stone reflexology & prompted my to further explore this modality.  This video prepared me to take a practical course in hot stone reflexology.  It inspired me to purchase stones and a heating case and I now am offering Hot Stone Reflexology at The Hour Spa in Austintown, Ohio.
